rComments: Stephanie is the kindest, most caring professor I have had the pleasure of learning from. During the pandemic she quickly and effectively switched everything online and made TONS of accommodations for students that were struggling. She really cares, is really fun, and loves Kaylor. Highly recommend, but beware of late classes.

Amazing! She's a new professor but I would take a class taught by her again in a heartbeat. She is so passionate about what she is teaching & it is really clear she cares about the topics discussed. She gave us all the readings online which was so thoughtful & her lectures aren't "mandatory" but you will 100% want to go even if it's a 7-10!
